        public String getTraversalSource()
        Description copied from interface: Translator
        Get the TraversalSource representation rooting this translator. For string-based translators (Translator.ScriptTranslator), this is typically a "g". For java-based translators (Translator.StepTranslator), this is typically the TraversalSource instance which the Traversal will be built from.
        Specified by:
